freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Had to take otc antihistamines for runny nose, watery eyes. Have a very inflamed, bright red, upper left ear that must have been a spider bite or something.
Headaches and i normally never have. May be because of pollen. Also really bad exhaustion but i work 8 to 10 hr days. Rhinitis that i always have.

Sneezing, cough, sore throat, runny nose, watery eyes yesterday & today. But temperature only 97.2 and I'm feeling better this afternoon. I assume common cold. Stayed home from work to not pass it to others. Rested.
